des:
Do you like challenges!?
Let's have a challenge in Mathematics.
Subtraction Game challenges your math skills in subtracting two numbers. You'll be given two random numbers to subtract. Then, you shall be asked to respond with the subtraction result. It is not necessary but if you play this game on an Echo Show 10 device (3rd Gen), you get some cool motion responses.
